room_title: Escape room "The (Un)Common room" by Escape on Purpose in Raleigh - Durham
review: This is the best escape room I have done so far. The staff is amazing and so friendly not to mention helpful! The rooms are original and very interesting, 10/10 fully recommend everyone try out their rooms at least once in their lives!!

room_title: Escape room "The (Un)Common room" by Escape on Purpose in Raleigh - Durham
review: We had a great time! Super friendly staff and well made escape room!!

room_title: Escape room "The (Un)Common room" by Escape on Purpose in Raleigh - Durham
review: Such a fun and challenging escape room! Our group had done other escape rooms and we all agreed this one was the most fun and interesting of all the ones we'd tried before. We did the Un Common room, and now can't wait to try the others!!
